content: Where can I get a link to the phonebank debrief form?  Also, where are the instructions to help with audio issues for data captains?
PLEASE FILL OUT DEBRIEF FORM HERE: https://forms.gle/6XihvVxwqpvrDaJg6. If calls are national or not state specific, select “national” under the state question.
This document has lots of tech type help.  See if this does it for you:  https://docs.google.com/document/d/1_AR1eDeagagfF7O5eQ9QcakuVWeK6gYTurJuqCKK1bQ/edit
